TRLine - Interface in org.proteininformationresource.siterule.model
Author: Chuming Chen
University of Delaware
Center for Bioinformatics and Computational Biology
Date: July 12, 2013

The TR (Trigger) line of this Site Rule, which describes which (selected) sequence analysis features trigger the application of this Site Rule.Each feature name should appear only once in the TR line in all the Site Rules, as one type of feature is expected to trigger only one rule.
